{
  "stem": "15962.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it, it-- the next step was so much more abrupt and severe that in a way, my impressions of the ghetto have been partly erased by the experience that I had later on during the war.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my mother had to work, I think, in a laundry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had-- have gone to kind of a daycare.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a school that housed other children-- in this case, boys.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was like a day student.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But theoretically, no educational teaching was permitted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So this had to be done in a clandestine way and under a guise of recreation or something like that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But there was this boys' school which created great bonds between children and the educators that-- of those who survived.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was an experience.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was unforgettable, especially those few privileged ones that were not deported into a concentration camp later on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "After a while, I was taken away from my mother and moved to one of these military barracks with, with boys of a similar age.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we started to do some cultural activities.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We published a magazine, and a weekly magazine, that was hand-written and hand-painted.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was a really a great cultural challenge for us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And recently, I was given copies of those magazines.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The originals survived and are now in Israel at Givat Haim in the Terezin Museum.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were exhibited recently in Stockholm and Prague and other countries.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And because-- and I'm now going back again, because this is a linkage.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "When we were restricted to play outdoors a lot or to visit sports fields and play soccer, we kind of drew inside of our apartments or rooms and played with little figurines of soldiers.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
